  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      An observational study to assess the BIS reported level of sedation of patients with&#xD;
      traumatic brain injury in the ICU.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients admitted to Aberdeen ICU with severe traumatic brain injury will have a BIS&#xD;
      electrode placed and observed for 24 hours. The study team will be blinded to the result, so&#xD;
      not to influence treatment.&#xD;
&#xD;
      All clinical care is at the discretion of the clinical team.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
